#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you double-click on a specific entry in the list of defined search "
#| "providers, the details for that entry are shown in a popup dialog. In "
#| "addition to the descriptive name for the item, you can also see the "
#| "<acronym>URI</acronym> which is used, as well as the associated shortcuts "
